&lt;p&gt;Squarespace has helped entrepreneurs build our digital presence for over two decades. As one of the world&#39;s largest domain providers, we are a trusted partner in one of the most consequential decisions any new business makes: choosing how they show up online.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Head of Domains and Email will run the Domains and Email businesses as a business within a business and with ownership of product strategy, P&amp;amp;L, team, and commercial outcomes. This is a GM-model leadership role. You set the vision, build the org, own the numbers, and drive execution end to end. You will report directly to the President.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;AI is fundamentally reshaping how people discover, register, manage, and derive value from domain names and DNS infrastructure. This role is a rare opportunity to lead that transformation at a meaningful scale and to define the very first step of every entrepreneur’s digital journey.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;You&#39;ll Get To...&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Business Ownership&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Own the Domains business end to end: strategy, P&amp;amp;L, headcount, organizational design, and long-range planning.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Set a compelling multi-year vision and translate it into annual operating plans with clear milestones, budgets, and accountability structures.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Own the commercial strategy: pricing, packaging, acquisition, retention, and expansion — including cross-sell and upsell into adjacent Squarespace products in close partnership with Marketing, Customer Operations, and Partnerships.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead strategic partnerships with registries, resellers, channel partners, and technology vendors.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Product Strategy &amp;amp; Execution&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Drive a differentiated product strategy for Domains — deepening customer experiences, accelerating innovation, and integrating the Domains business into a cohesive, entrepreneur-focused product ecosystem across Squarespace.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop scalable customer research practices that surface insights to drive roadmap prioritization, new product investment, and future strategy.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate closely with Engineering to build a high-trust, high-output environment for operational and delivery excellence.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;&lt;strong&gt;AI Transformation&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Own the AI transformation agenda for Domains, not just shipping AI features, but fundamentally reimagining the business model, operations, and competitive advantages through AI.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build an AI-native team where AI fluency is a baseline expectation and where humans and agents work together to move faster and deliver more customer value.&lt;/li&gt;
